function Start()
	--player line
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(conv_PlayerNo, idSelf)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("StartTheater01", idSelf, idSelf)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("StartTheater02", idSelf, idSelf)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("StartTheater03", idSelf, idSelf)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	--Villagers all feel better and attend Lau's body
	--Villagers A, D, G
	idActorCloneA00 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(SickVillagerA00, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorCloneA00) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(idActorCloneA00, 1, true)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActorCloneA00, false, true)
	    Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorCloneA00, SickVillagerA01, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorCloneA00, SickVillagerA01)
	    Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorCloneA00, 0, SickVillagerA01, false)
	end
	
	idActorCloneD00 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(SickVillagerD00, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorCloneD00) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(idActorCloneD00, 2, true)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActorCloneD00, false, true)
	    Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorCloneD00, SickVillagerD01, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorCloneD00, SickVillagerD01)
	    Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorCloneD00, 0, SickVillagerD01, false)
	end
	
	idActorCloneG00 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(SickVillagerG00, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorCloneG00) then
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActorCloneG00, false, true)
	    Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorCloneG00, SickVillagerG01, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idActorCloneG00, SickVillagerG01)
	    Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idActorCloneG00, 0, SickVillagerG01, false)
	end
	
end
